"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"sublist_other\">",
"        7.5 to 10 mg/kg&nbsp;every 8 hours,&nbsp;or 20 to 30 mg/kg every 24 hours",
"       </td>",
"       <td class=\"sublist_other\">",
